title: What is the song that goes something like 'nana nananananana nana' three times, and and also goes like 'oh naaaaa oh nanananaaaaa oh naaaa oh nanana'? - Quora

response.answer_text: There have been so many “Nana nanananana Nana” songs over the years, I find it difficult to answer this question. However, while looking, I heard many old tunes that I hadn’t heard in years, so you made my day. I’ll share a few to help make your day too! First is Jim South in 1969, singing the song, The Games People Play.  The Alan Parson’s Project in 1980 sang the same song, The Games People Play.  This answer could go on and on and on and …. Ok, now I’m pretty tired of Nana nananana songs. If it’s not in one of these top 50 nananana songs, I give up!  I sure hope the song you were looking for is on my list of songs. Was it?
